<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA522_01_SU_0003_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <!-- <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema522_00.css" /> -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema522_01_su.css" />
</head>

<body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema522_01_su_0003">
        <section class="title type2">
            <h2 data-type="1" data-text="자기주도 2">
                <span class="blue line" lang="y">배운 내용을 떠올려요</span>
                <span lang="y">카드를 선택하여 이전에 배운 내용을 확인해 봅시다.</span>
            </h2>
        </section>

        <section class="contents">
            <ul class="letCheck">
                <li>
                    <div class="cover pointer large"></div>
                    <div class="front">
                        <p class="f32b" lang="y">분수만큼은 <br />얼마인지 알아보기</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="back">
                        <p class="f32b fraction_row" lang="y"><span>8의</span>
                            <span class="fraction_box"><span>1</span><span>4</span></span> 는 2
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <div class="cover pointer large"></div>
                    <div class="front">
                        <p class="f32b" lang="y">대분수를 가분수로,<br /> 가분수를 대분수로 나타내기</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="back">
                        <p class="f32b fraction_row" lang="y"><span>2</span>
                            <span class="fraction_box"><span>7</span><span>9</span></span><span>=</span>
                            <span class="fraction_box"><span>25</span><span>9</span></span>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <div class="cover pointer large"></div>
                    <div class="front">
                        <p class="f32b" lang="y">분모가 같은<br /> 진분수의 덧셈하기</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="back">
                        <p class="f32b fraction_row" lang="y"><span
                                class="fraction_box"><span>2</span><span>8</span></span><span>+</span><span
                                class="fraction_box"><span>3</span><span>8</span></span><span>=</span><span
                                class="fraction_box"><span>5</span><span>8</span></span></p>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <div class="cover pointer large"></div>
                    <div class="front">
                        <p class="f32b" lang="y">약분하기</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="back">
                        <p class="f32b mixed_fraction" lang="y">
                            <span class="fraction_box"><span>12</span><span>24</span></span><span>약분 =</span>

                            <span class="flex align_end">
                                <span class="fraction_box gap_20"><span>6</span><span>12</span></span>
                                <span class="mr_8">,</span>
                                <span class="fraction_box gap_20"><span>4</span><span>8</span></span>
                                <span class="mr_8">,</span>
                                <span class="fraction_box gap_20"><span>3</span><span>6</span></span>
                                <span class="mr_8">,</span>
                                <span class="fraction_box gap_20"><span>2</span><span>4</span></span>
                                <span class="mr_8">,</span>
                                <span class="fraction_box gap_20"><span>1</span><span>2</span></span>
                            </span>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </section>


        <div class="bubble_charactor" data-charactor="1" style="display: none;">
            <div class="bubble" data-point-position="bottom left">
                <p lang="y">카드를 한 번 더 선택하면</p>
                <p lang="y">내용을 볼 수 있어요.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="btn_area">
            <!-- 불필요한 태그 제외 후 사용 -->
            <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
            <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>